    "description": "<strong> 你的健康就是时间 </strong><br><strong>必须杀死才能获得更多时间</strong><br><br>&quot;MULLET MADJACK 发生的背景是 90 年代，更准确点，是 2090 年。这是一款第一人称视角动作游戏，风格狂乱，将玩家带入一个复古的动画世界。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/d9cfb71417271eccfebcda16bd03def6.poster.avif?t=1765391765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/d9cfb71417271eccfebcda16bd03def6.webm?t=1765391765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/d9cfb71417271eccfebcda16bd03def6.mp4?t=1765391765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> 在未来，人和互联网会融合为新物种。这个新物种每 10 秒就需要多巴胺，否则就会死去！<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/cedbe68d1a66384caa31d43a28543da0.avif?t=1765391765\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br> 世界现在由超级富有的人工智能机器人“巨富机器人”统治，<br> 而那些为了杀死机器人而将自己 10 秒钟的生命置之度外的人被称为“制裁者”！ <br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/5962975627675c32964387697fe0fe23.avif?t=1765391765\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><br><br> • 你是鲻鱼头疯狂杰克，你需要杀死敌人来恢复自己 10 秒的生命！ <br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/5e770474d52370215cb456c0b6152eb0.poster.avif?t=1765391765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/5e770474d52370215cb456c0b6152eb0.webm?t=1765391765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/5e770474d52370215cb456c0b6152eb0.mp4?t=1765391765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br> • 每个章节都有随机生成的关卡，里面布满了令人兴奋的新障碍！<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/13ae07016e84df941f5fd9b7aeba44f7.poster.avif?t=1765391765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/13ae07016e84df941f5fd9b7aeba44f7.webm?t=1765391765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/13ae07016e84df941f5fd9b7aeba44f7.mp4?t=1765391765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br> • 每一层楼都有精心设计的战斗场景，充满 roguelike 元素，你需要巧妙地构造自己的角色。 <br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/283018ed0f2c247a932f9435423844c2.poster.avif?t=1765391765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/283018ed0f2c247a932f9435423844c2.webm?t=1765391765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/283018ed0f2c247a932f9435423844c2.mp4?t=1765391765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br> • 打败神秘的幕后黑手，体验终极老派动画剧情！ <br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/dae1018119aca10e23380d5cac68a1ef.poster.avif?t=1765391765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/dae1018119aca10e23380d5cac68a1ef.webm?t=1765391765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111190/extras/dae1018119aca10e23380d5cac68a1ef.mp4?t=1765391765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br> <br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>亮点：</strong></h2> • 让人重温旧日快节奏街机游戏的刺激感，每一刻都充满了多巴胺飙升的愉悦体验<br> • 采用全动画战斗场景，配合复古动漫过场动画<br> • 超过 50 种升级道具，改变你的游玩方式<br> • 在程序化的无尽模式中永远游玩<br> • 90 年代虚拟 PC 游戏盒子开箱体验<br> • 重温 80 和 90 年代的腥风血雨<br> <br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[/b] 易玩性： [/b]</h2> 完全支持手柄，并有按键和按钮重新绑定、鼠标灵敏度、紫血模式、禁用视角抖动和闪光、自定义瞄准等选项，以及音效、音乐和语音的自定义音量控制。",
